properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 31 at 2:08AM PST until February 1 at 7:00AM PST by NWS Seattle WA
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 40-50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Southwest Interior, Tacoma Area, East Puget Sound
Lowlands, Bellevue and Vicinity, Seattle and Vicinity and
Bremerton and Vicinity.

* WHEN...From 10 AM this morning to 7 AM PST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The strongest winds are expected to be late
this afternoon through this evening.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM THIS MORNING TO 7 AM PST SATURDAY
